24/*
25 * Redefine CHECK here so cppcheck "sees" the define.
26 */
27#ifndef CHECK
28#define CHECK(op) \
29 do { result = (op); \
30 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) goto cleanup; \
31 } while (0)
32#endif
33
34#define RRTYPE_WKS_ATTRIBUTES (0)
35
36static isc_mutex_t wks_lock;
37
38static void init_lock(void) {
39 isc_mutex_init(&wks_lock);
40}
41
42static bool
43mygetprotobyname(const char *name, long *proto) {
44 struct protoent *pe;
45
46 LOCK(&wks_lock);
47 pe = getprotobyname(name);
48 if (pe != NULL)
49 *proto = pe->p_proto;
50 UNLOCK(&wks_lock);
51 return (pe != NULL);
52}
53
54static bool
55mygetservbyname(const char *name, const char *proto, long *port) {
56 struct servent *se;
57
58 LOCK(&wks_lock);
59 se = getservbyname(name, proto);
60 if (se != NULL)
61 *port = ntohs(se->s_port);
62 UNLOCK(&wks_lock);
63 return (se != NULL);
64}

72static inline isc_result_t
73fromtext_in_wks(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
74 static isc_once_t once = ISC_ONCE_INIT;
75 isc_token_t token;
76 isc_region_t region;
77 struct in_addr addr;
78 char *e;
79 long proto;
80 unsigned char bm[8*1024]; /* 64k bits */
81 long port;
82 long maxport = -1;
83 const char *ps = NULL;
84 unsigned int n;
85 char service[32];
86 int i;
87 isc_result_t result;
88
89 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
90 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
91
92 UNUSED(type);
93 UNUSED(origin);
94 UNUSED(options);
95 UNUSED(rdclass);
96 UNUSED(callbacks);
97
98 RUNTIME_CHECK(isc_once_do(&once, init_lock) == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
99
100#ifdef _WIN32
101 {
102 WORD wVersionRequested;
103 WSADATA wsaData;
104 int err;
105
106 wVersionRequested = MAKEWORD(2, 0);
107
108 err = WSAStartup(wVersionRequested, &wsaData );
109 if (err != 0)
110 return (ISC_R_FAILURE);
111 }
112#endif
113
114 /*
115 * IPv4 dotted quad.
116 */
117 CHECK(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
118 false));
119
120 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
121 if (inet_pton(AF_INET, DNS_AS_STR(token), &addr) != 1)
122 CHECKTOK(DNS_R_BADDOTTEDQUAD);
123 if (region.length < 4)
124 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
125 memmove(region.base, &addr, 4);
126 isc_buffer_add(target, 4);
127
128 /*
129 * Protocol.
130 */
131 CHECK(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
132 false));
133
134 proto = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
135 if (*e == 0)
136 ;
137 else if (!mygetprotobyname(DNS_AS_STR(token), &proto))
138 CHECKTOK(DNS_R_UNKNOWNPROTO);
139
140 if (proto < 0 || proto > 0xff)
141 CHECKTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
142
143 if (proto == IPPROTO_TCP)
144 ps = "tcp";
145 else if (proto == IPPROTO_UDP)
146 ps = "udp";
147
148 CHECK(uint8_tobuffer(proto, target));
149
150 memset(bm, 0, sizeof(bm));
151 do {
152 CHECK(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
153 isc_tokentype_string, true));
154 if (token.type != isc_tokentype_string)
155 break;
156
157 /*
158 * Lowercase the service string as some getservbyname() are
159 * case sensitive and the database is usually in lowercase.
160 */
161 strlcpy(service, DNS_AS_STR(token), sizeof(service));
162 for (i = strlen(service) - 1; i >= 0; i--)
163 if (isupper(service[i]&0xff))
164 service[i] = tolower(service[i]&0xff);
165
166 port = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
167 if (*e == 0)
168 ;
169 else if (!mygetservbyname(service, ps, &port) &&
170 !mygetservbyname(DNS_AS_STR(token), ps, &port))
171 CHECKTOK(DNS_R_UNKNOWNSERVICE);
172 if (port < 0 || port > 0xffff)
173 CHECKTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
174 if (port > maxport)
175 maxport = port;
176 bm[port / 8] |= (0x80 >> (port % 8));
177 } while (1);
178
179 /*
180 * Let upper layer handle eol/eof.
181 */
182 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
183
184 n = (maxport + 8) / 8;
185 result = mem_tobuffer(target, bm, n);
186
187 cleanup:
188#ifdef _WIN32
189 WSACleanup();
190#endif
191
192 return (result);
193}

195static inline isc_result_t
196totext_in_wks(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
197 isc_region_t sr;
198 unsigned short proto;
199 char buf[sizeof("65535")];
200 unsigned int i, j;
201
202 UNUSED(tctx);
203
204 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
205 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
206 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 5);
207
208 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
209 RETERR(inet_totext(AF_INET, &sr, target));
210 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
211
212 proto = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
213 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", proto);
214 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
215 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
216 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
217
218 INSIST(sr.length <= 8*1024);
219 for (i = 0; i < sr.length; i++) {
220 if (sr.base[i] != 0)
221 for (j = 0; j < 8; j++)
222 if ((sr.base[i] & (0x80 >> j)) != 0) {
223 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf),
224 "%u", i * 8 + j);
225 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
226 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
227 }
228 }
229
230 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
231}

233static inline isc_result_t
234fromwire_in_wks(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
235 isc_region_t sr;
236 isc_region_t tr;
237
238 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
239 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
240
241 UNUSED(type);
242 UNUSED(dctx);
243 UNUSED(options);
244 UNUSED(rdclass);
245
246 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
247 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tr);
248
249 if (sr.length < 5)
250 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
251 if (sr.length > 8 * 1024 + 5)
252 return (DNS_R_EXTRADATA);
253 if (tr.length < sr.length)
254 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
255
256 memmove(tr.base, sr.base, sr.length);
257 isc_buffer_add(target, sr.length);
258 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
259
260 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
261}

263static inline isc_result_t
264towire_in_wks(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
265 isc_region_t sr;
266
267 UNUSED(cctx);
268
269 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
270 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
271 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
272
273 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
274 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
275}

277static inline int
278compare_in_wks(ARGS_COMPARE) {
279 isc_region_t r1;
280 isc_region_t r2;
281
282 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
283 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
284 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
285 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
286 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
287 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
288
289 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
290 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
291 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
292}
293
294static inline isc_result_t
295fromstruct_in_wks(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
296 dns_rdata_in_wks_t *wks = source;
297 uint32_t a;
298
299 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
300 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
301 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
302 REQUIRE(wks->common.rdtype == type);
303 REQUIRE(wks->common.rdclass == rdclass);
304 REQUIRE((wks->map != NULL && wks->map_len <= 8*1024) ||
305 wks->map_len == 0);
306
307 UNUSED(type);
308 UNUSED(rdclass);
309
310 a = ntohl(wks->in_addr.s_addr);
311 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(a, target));
312 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(wks->protocol, target));
313 return (mem_tobuffer(target, wks->map, wks->map_len));
314}
315
316static inline isc_result_t
317tostruct_in_wks(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
318 dns_rdata_in_wks_t *wks = target;
319 uint32_t n;
320 isc_region_t region;
321
322 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
323 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
324 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
325
326 wks->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
327 wks->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
328 ISC_LINK_INIT(&wks->common, link);
329
330 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
331 n = uint32_fromregion(&region);
332 wks->in_addr.s_addr = htonl(n);
333 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
334 wks->protocol = uint8_fromregion(&region);
335 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
336 wks->map_len = region.length;
337 wks->map = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
338 if (wks->map == NULL)
339 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
340 wks->mctx = mctx;
341 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
342}
343
344static inline void
345freestruct_in_wks(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
346 dns_rdata_in_wks_t *wks = source;
347
348 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
349 REQUIRE(wks->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_wks);
350 REQUIRE(wks->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
351
352 if (wks->mctx == NULL)
353 return;
354
355 if (wks->map != NULL)
356 isc_mem_free(wks->mctx, wks->map);
357 wks->mctx = NULL;
358}

369 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);

372static inline isc_result_t
373digest_in_wks(ARGS_DIGEST) {
374 isc_region_t r;
375
376 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_wks);
377 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
378
379 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
380
381 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
382}
